        "\n",
        "The published 17.81 was somewhere between these two protocols. The 17.81→15.38 \"improvement\" claimed in v17 was **~93% protocol fix**.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Phase 1a/b/c: Multi-k F1 + label-efficiency sweep\n",
        "\n",
        "Honest probe of v17 best ckpts across budgets and seeds.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Mode | 100% | 50% | 20% | 10% | 5% |\n",
