        "| E2E | 15.08 ± 0.10 | 15.85 ± 0.55 | 17.85 ± 0.63 | 19.62 ± 1.36 | 21.55 ± 1.52 |\n",
        "\n",
        "Multi-k F1 on v17 frozen: F1@k=10 0.71, k=20 0.82, k=30 0.92, k=50 0.92.\n",
